<th scope="row" style="padding-right: 1em">Years&#160;of service</th>
<td>
<div class="plainlist">
<ul>
<li>Colonial militia: 1757 (Connecticut), 1775 (Connecticut, Massachusetts)</li>
<li>Continental Army (United Colonies/United States): 1775–1780</li>
<li>British Army: 1780–1781</li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
